 Bonnie Chung's new book, Miso Tasty / One of the essential ingredients in Japanese food is miso, made from soybean paste. Miso is increasingly appearing in non-Japanese dishes, bringing a blast of umami wherever it goes. Bonnie Chung's new book, Miso Tasty (Pavilion, £14.99) has 60 recipes to get you started. SEEDLIP SPIRITS 





 
