 The Cultured Food Company. Ruby Red Sauerkraut / SuperValu's Food Academy supports fledgling food producers as they grow their businesses and also makes a wider range of Irish-made food products available to Irish consumers. The delicious Ruby Red Sauerkraut from the Cultured Food Company (from €4.85) is a way to introduce fermented, gut-friendly food into your diet. Irish Independent 
